Description: This Jaguar is fast becoming a modern classic. Its timeless curves make it one of the most beautiful coupes Jaguar (or anyone else) has every produced.  It is a true celebration of luxury and performance.  The 5.0 V8 packs an all mighty punch, perfectly accentuated with the lightweight, all alluminium, monocoque chassis.  The interior is a statement of quality and comfort.  Unlike many of its sports car rivals the XK is an amazing grand tourer as well as being an awesome sports car.  Our car is a delight, it boasts a full service history (apart from 2020 when it was in lockdown), the gorgeous 20 inch studded alloy wheels and Bowers and Willkes Sound.  We have carried out a major service and MOT, its in fantastic condition and still smells of fresh leather.  It's the perfect sports car to waft about in, knowing that it can only solidify its position as one of the British classic sports car of all time.

Description: Our Seat Leon Cupra TSI DSG is the perfect combination of performance, beauty and practicality. The obvious palace to start with this car is the performance specification, with an absolutely thrilling 300 BHP and low to the road feel, performance tyres, steering and throttle response, gear shifts mode, dynamic chassis control and mechanical limited slip differential, this car is made for high octane thrills. Add to that the stunning looks, meticulously designed with a streamlined and modern figure finished in Mediterranean Blue with 19" Cupra Machined alloy wheels with red brake callipers, dual exhaust  pipes and the whole car embellished with Cupra logos and styling throughout, this car looks the part too. The interior has a lot to offer too with many driver conveniences to make the driving experience that much better. The entertainment system is fantastic, having Apple Carplay and Android Auto. The car also has front and rear parking sensors,auto headlights, rain sensing wipers, LED interior illumination pack, a flat bottom perforated leather steering wheel, sports seats and aluminium finishing throughout to add to the sporting yet comfortable feel of the interior. All of our vehicles are prepared to an extremely high standard and this car will come with 2 keys and will also have a fresh MOT ready for its new owner with an industry leading 6 month warranty.
